                <h1>Roger Federer: The Tennis Legend</h1>
                <p>Roger Federer, a tennis legend, has captivated fans with his elegant playing style and unparalleled achievements. Born in Switzerland, he turned professional in 1998 and quickly rose to prominence, winning 20 Grand Slam titles and countless accolades. Known for his sportsmanship and dedication, Federer remains a beloved figure in the world of sports.</p>
